description: This file contains unit tests for the UserSettings module, utilizing Google Test and Google Mock frameworks. It tests various user setting handlers such as audio descriptions, language preferences, viewing restrictions, and content PINs, by mocking dependencies and verifying expected behaviors and error codes.
